data.description: Charming 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom All-Brick Georgian home located in the Historical La Grange Park, IL, within the coveted Yena Park section! This updated gem boasts a newer eat-in kitchen featuring stunning cabinets, Silestone countertops, and stainless steel appliances. Enjoy the elegance of hardwood floors and custom blinds throughout. The first floor showcases an updated full bathroom with a tile walk-in shower.    Upstairs, you have 3 generously-sized, beautifully appointed bedrooms along with another fully renovated bathroom. The sizable finished basement adds flexibility to the space, while recent upgrades include a new hot water tank, dryer, furnace, and approximately 5-year-old roof. Additionally, the sump pump is equipped with a battery backup for added peace of mind.    Step through the sliding glass door to a lovely, completely fenced backyard highlighted by a paver patio-a perfect retreat. A NEWLY BUILT 2-car garage with new concrete slab and side drive enhance convenience and functionality.    This home also boasts proximity to excellent grade schools, middle schools, and high schools. Walk to nearby grade schools, forest preserve trails, and parks, while enjoying convenient access to shopping amenities
